         :ElseIf at≤pw-ind ⍝ Or perhaps on a single separate line if they don't fit on the same one
             mat,←nl,(ind⍴' '),at↑sql ⍝? Are they still/more readable?
         :Else ⍝ If we have to, split them all up on multiple lines
