             at←¯1+(t∧0=-⌿+\'()'∘.=∆clean sql)⍳1
             m←↑nl ∆cut((pw-ind),ind)See at↑sql
             mat,←(at=0)↓nl,nl ∆sew ∆dtr¨↓(-(0,ind)+⍴m)↑m
             sql←at↓sql
